# BMAD artifacts (planning + story files) are tracked so collaborators
# share the same source of truth. Substrate runs write into this tree
# during dispatch — commit the artifacts you want shared, leave
# ephemeral/transient run outputs uncommitted.

# Runtime state
.substrate/
amendment-delta-*.md

# Build outputs
dist/
coverage/
*.tgz
*.tsbuildinfo

